content: I think those tips are really helpful, especially the one about taking breaks and celebrating small wins. I've been trying to prioritize my well-being lately, especially since I had that panic attack in the middle of the night a while back, which was really scary and left me feeling shaken. I've been making an effort to take care of myself, but it's good to be reminded of the importance of self-care when working on a big project like this. Do you have any suggestions for how I can prioritize self-care while still meeting my deadline?
